e bearish signals cluster around a single macro narrative (2026/27 forward supply). The 2026/27 crop is not deliverable now. The physical tightness is. If this trade is compelling at all, it belongs 60-90 days later when the bearish macro supply materializes into visible stocks. Today, the risk-reward at support, with expensive IV, in a range-bound regime, with three active bullish catalysts, does not meet minimum standards for a directional short. VERDICT: NO TRADE.
